 across campus. Wouldn’t it be nice to work on your geospatial projects a
 round peers who actually understand what you’re doing? Come work in the 
 same space with other geo people\, get feedback\, ask questions\, and answ
 er questions.\n \n\nConcepts Covered: Coworking\, Getting Help\, Making Pr
 ogress\, Crossing Things Off the To-Do list\n \n\nSpeaker: Community\n \n\
