UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51509000232876
DESCRIPTION:Location: DataLab Classroom - room 360 Shields Library\n \n\nD
 escription: This question and answer session will allow participants to as
 k questions about applying for jobs and working in the geospatial field at
  a variety of institutions.\n \n\nConcepts Covered: Careers\n \n\nSpeaker:
  Coordinated by Naomi Kalman\n\nGuest speakers will include geospatial pro
 fessionals working in state\, federal\, and local government\; private ind
 ustry\; and research universities. Join us for a no-host lunch at Gunrock 
 Pub (UCD Silo) after the event.\n \n\nPrerequisites: No prior experience i
 s required.\n \n\nSoftware Required: No software is required.\n \n\nPlease
  RSVP.
